            <div type="slide">
                <head>La convergence</head>
                <!--<p>But convergence is now on everyone's digital agenda. When you make a mashup
                    combining <list>
                        <item>a GIS database about places in the Aegean sea</item>
                        <item> a historical gazeteer of placenames in the same area</item>
